    <para id="para-00008">
      Not everyone embraced George Whitefield and other New Lights. Many established Old Lights decried the way the new evangelical religions appealed to people’s passions, rather than to traditional religious values. The two illustrations below present two very different visions of George Whitefield (<link target-id="CNX_History_04_04_Whitefield">Figure 4.14</link>).
    </para>
